CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 27, 1954, pg. 21 reads: "Herron Hill P-TA Rallies to Keep Teen Canteen - Check Room - The controlled atmosphere of the school gives way to an easy informality at canteen time."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys and girls, including seated girl wearing light colored short sleeve shirt, holding hanger, in coat check room in Herron Hill Junior High School
